        <div class="label">a) The Na+ and Cl- ions will evaporate into the air with the H2O molecules.</div><br/>
        <input name="question" type="radio" value="incorrect"/>
        <div class="label">b) The Na+ ions will evaporate with the water, leaving behind the Cl- ions. </div><br/>
        <input name="question" type="radio" value="incorrect"/>
